data.description: Need concessions? Sellers are open to buyer assistance - let's chat!! 2020 home that has been lightly lived in and   very well cared for just under two years. 3 bedroom, two bath single story. Spacious floorplan with kitchen,   dining and living open for entertaining and spending easy quality time. Stainless appliances, granite counters.   Large owner's suite with ensuite bathroom; huge walk-in shower, tons of storage and counter space.   Private backyard with covered patio. Make this adorable home yours for under $350,000.   Seller may need short lease back. Conveniently located with close proximity to 130 and making   the airport a 30 minute commute; shopping, entertainment & dining easily accessible within 10   minutes of you; Tesla is a short 20 minute drive; Amazon is 15 minutes and downtown Austin is  mere 40 minutes. Washer, dryer, fridge included; some  furnishings negotiable. No showings on Wednesdays
